				<p>You either need to change the motor to a *Brushed* DC motor. Or you need to change the motor driver to a *Brushless* motor driver. You could easily drive the ESC from an Arduino. It just needs a [PWM signal](http://www.brookshiresoftware.com/rd_how_servos_work.htm).</p>
